node.text: The Cantopop legend will livestream his concert – hosted by actor Lawrence Cheng – on YouTube, Instagram and Facebook at 5pm SGT this Sunday. His aim? Simply to bring cheer to those affected by COVID-19, especially folks who lost their jobs. 😔✊ #SamHui #Cantopop #singer #music #HongKong #livestream #concert #weekend #positivevibes #CNAlifestyle (Pic: Instagram/samhuiofficial)
Let me guess what he's gonna sing about : $, workers .. old tunes? Or new +ve tunes?😝
